com.nokia.dempsy.cluster
Interface DisruptibleSession

All Known Implementing Classes:
LocalClusterSessionFactory.LocalSession, ZookeeperSession
public interface DisruptibleSession

This interface is used in tests. Given an implementation of a ClusterInfoSession ALSO implements DisruptibleSession, a test can use 'disrupt' to cause a problem in the session that will cause it to automatically reset. For example, in the case of Zookeeper it closes the client.
